Package: hathiTools
Title: Access the Hathi Trust Bookworm and Extracted Features Files from R
Version: 0.0.0.9001
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Xavier",
           family = "Marquez",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "marquez.x@gmail.com")
Description: The package allows one to query the Hathi Trust Digital Library Bookworm and Workset Builder, as well as to download the "extracted features" and metadata files for more than 17 million digitized volumes.
